Package: basecase
Title: Base-R Functions for Mimicking dplyr's `case_match()` and `case_when()`
Version: 0.2025.3.12
Authors@R: 
    person("Yea-Hung", "Chen", , "yea-hung.chen@ucsf.edu", role = "aut)
Description: Base-R functions for mimicking dplyr's `case_match()` and `case_when()`. Unlike `case_match()` and `case_when()`, `base_match()` and `base_when()` return factors.
License: `use_mit_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
